raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do social_post(\"mabel_clubs\")
Mabel: img: other/7
Mabel: Babe look what Mom sent me yesterday 🤣
Player: Is that my old ball?
Mabel: It is!
Mabel: She found it under my bed while she was cleaning up lol
Mabel: You would lose it so often 🙄
Player: True 😁
Player: I remember your room and bed lol
Player: The first time I saw it I thought I was like what the
Player: She really likes pink...
Mabel: Heyyy, you got your dirty ball in my nice room omg
Mabel: There was mud everywhere, we had to buy new sheets 🥺
Mabel: I cried for like a week 😂
Mabel: You even made shoeprints on the couch 😂
Player: That was you!
Mabel: Nuh uh 😇 I was a perfect child!
Mabel: 🤥
Player: 🤣
Mabel: Can't believe I've seriously known you for all my life 😆
Mabel: As far back as I can even remember, you've always been around
- Hopefully far into the future too! [#love]
	Player: Hopefully far into the future too!
	Mabel: You're so adorable 🥰
	Mabel: PinkThought: I'm going to enjoy every moment with you
	Mabel: 🙈
	Player: Babe?
	Mabel: Sorry, just shy hehe
- With that many complaint about me, you sure you want me around more? 😁 [#distrust]
	Player: With that many complaint about me, you sure you want me around more? 😁
	Mabel: Of course silly
	Mabel: I'll complain about you my whole life but I wouldn't want anyone else hehe
	Mabel: Ack, don't make me say these things out loud 😳
	Mabel: So embarassing omg 🙃
Mabel: Since mom was going through the divorce, she was glad you appeared in my life
Mabel: She said that at least I'd have a little man to take care of me while she figured things out
Mabel: Seriously she was so grateful 🥹
Player: I guess you can call me dad now 😌
Mabel: No way, shut up omg 😂
Mabel: img: mabel/73
Mabel: I'm so glad you aren't my dad
Mabel: You're a lot better than my dad ever was 🥰
Player: I'm glad to have helped 😇
if Story.mabel_desire <= 0:
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: Thought: When mom was dropping me off
	Mabel: Thought: She told me that I was old enough to... \"be with a man\"
	Mabel: Thought: Her lecture embarassed me so much
	do heart(2)
	Mabel: PinkThought: She told me the right guy will eventually come along and that love would hurt a little at first
	Mabel: PinkThought: But over time I'd feel like I belong to them and that feeling would slowly become the best thing ever
	Mabel: PinkThought: I felt like I totally understood
	Mabel: PinkThought: So what are you waiting for...
	Player: Mabes? 
	Player: You still there?
	do heart(0)
	Mabel: I'm here 😊
Mabel: I'm glad I barely have any homework today
Mabel: So we could catch up 🥰
Mabel: PinkThought: Maybe I should do it today?...
Mabel: img: mabel/74
Mabel: Hi there! 🙈
Mabel: Thought: I hope you like these kind of pictures
Player: Hey 😍
Mabel: Thought: Maybe I should be taking more of these hehe
Mabel: Thought: I'll see if I can come up with some good ideas later
if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
	Mabel: Sure you don't want to come over?
	Mabel: It feels like every girl in my dorm has a boy over 🤭
	Mabel: I need my boy too 😚🩷
	Player: You think we'll fit on your bed? 😊
	Mabel: We'll make us fit 🥰
	Mabel: I'm compact sized but I'll let you squish me a little haha 😆
	Player: If I squish you anymore, then you'll become really small!
	Mabel: Somehow I don't mind it
else:
	Mabel: Would you take me out on a night time stroll?
	Mabel: I want to see what it's like to be out really late at night but y'know I'm... 🥲
	Player: Sure! We've never done anything like that before
	Mabel: You better hold my hand tightly and not let go though
	Player: I will!
	Mabel: Promise? No teasing either?? 😒
	Player: Promise!
	Mabel: Okay then 🥰 
	Mabel: I want to see what everyone's doing so late anyway!
Mabel: 🤭
Mabel: How are your days going babe?
if Story.mabel_trust < 50:
	Mabel: Made any new friends lately?
	Player: Not really!
	Player: I just sorta go to class and do what I can haha
	Player: What about you?
	Mabel: Mmmh.. maybe?
	Mabel: I feel I'm getting a lot of attention 🤔
	Mabel: Nina says it's a lot of guys that want to be my friend
	Mabel: But she did a whole air quotes thing when she said friend 😆
	Player: Lol
	Mabel: It sounded funny
	Mabel: Yeah not sure, maybe it's because of club week
else:
	Player: Not too eventful
	Mabel: Same here, feels like I'm a robot sometimes with all the homework lol 🤖
	Mabel: I hope we get to have more group hangouts with Naomi and the rest!
	Mabel: I had so much fun last time!
	Player: Same!
	Mabel: 🥰 I think it'll be nice every now and then
Mabel: I need to wake up early tomorrow for my class so I think I'll sleep now
Mabel: Miss you babe 😙
Player: Miss you too!
Mabel: I hope I get to see you soon!
Mabel: Nighty
Player: Night!
if Story.mabel_trust < 50:
	set PhoneUnlocks.leak = \"nina2\"
	do social_post(\"nina_recruiting\")
else:
	set PhoneUnlocks.leak = \"naomi1\"
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
